.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PLUGIN-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-plugin-list \- list active CLN plugins
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-plugin-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the list of active plugins from the Core Lightning daemon.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{name, active, dynamic}]
.fi
Returns an empty array when the daemon is not reachable.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-info (1),
.BR lightning-node-version (1)
